# .env Template - Copy and Fill These Values

## 🔐 Blockchain Configuration
PRIVATE_KEY=your_metamask_private_key_without_0x_prefix
BSCSCAN_API_KEY=get_from_https://bscscan.com/apis

## 🤖 AI & Telegram
GROQ_API_KEY=get_from_https://console.groq.com/keys
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=get_from_botfather_on_telegram
TELEGRAM_GROUP_ID=your_telegram_group_id

## 💾 Database (Optional)
MONGODB_URL=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/dbname

## 🌐 APIs
BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:3001
PORT=3001

## 📝 Deployed Contract Addresses (Fill after running: npm run deploy)
FACTORY_ADDRESS=get_after_deploy

---

## 🔴 IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTES:

1. ⚠️ NEVER commit this file to Git
2. ⚠️ NEVER share your PRIVATE_KEY with anyone
3. ⚠️ NEVER paste .env file into GitHub/Discord/Forums
4. ⚠️ This file is already in .gitignore (protected automatically)
5. ⚠️ Private key format: just the hex value (0x... is optional)

---

## 📋 How to Get Each Key:

### PRIVATE_KEY
- Open MetaMask → Settings → Security & Privacy → Show Private Key
- Enter password → Copy the key → Paste here

### BSCSCAN_API_KEY
- Go to: https://bscscan.com
- Sign up → Go to API-KEYs → Create New Key → Copy

### GROQ_API_KEY:
1. Go to: https://console.groq.com/keys
2. Login → Create API key → Copy

### TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN
- Open Telegram app
- Search for @BotFather
- Type: /newbot
- Follow instructions → Get token → Copy

### TELEGRAM_GROUP_ID
- Add your bot to a Telegram group
- Send message in group
- Go to: https://api.telegram.org/bot[YOUR_TOKEN]/getUpdates
- Find "chat": {"id": -123456789}
- Copy that negative number

### FACTORY_ADDRESS
- After running: npm run deploy
- Copy the "TokenFactory deployed to: 0x..." address
- Paste it here

---

## ✅ Test Your .env

Run this to verify everything works:
```bash
npm run deploy
# This will test your PRIVATE_KEY and BSCSCAN_API_KEY
```

Then run:
```bash
npm run backend
# This will test your BACKEND_URL and FACTORY_ADDRESS
```

Then run:
```bash
npm run agent
# This will test your TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN and OPENAI_API_KEY
```

---

If everything works, you're ready to launch! 🚀 Bzzzt! ⚡
